        "imageUrl": "https://media.githubusercontent.com/media/b94901099/Hanzi-Steps-Images/main/stories/pangu/img_story_pangu_59.png"
      },
      {
        "id": "sent_pangu_60",
        "text": "他的手臂，一天比一天有力。",
