        "imageUrl": "https://media.githubusercontent.com/media/b94901099/Hanzi-Steps-Images/main/stories/pangu/img_story_pangu_68.png"
      },
      {
        "id": "sent_pangu_69",
        "text": "他耗盡了所有的力氣，再也沒有力氣站著了。",
        "words": ["他", "耗", "盡", "所", "有", "力", "氣", "再", "也", "沒", "站"],
