        "imageUrl": "https://media.githubusercontent.com/media/b94901099/Hanzi-Steps-Images/main/stories/pangu/img_story_pangu_79.png"
      },
      {
        "id": "sent_pangu_80",
        "text": "他說話的聲音，變成了天上的雷。",
