        "imageUrl": "https://media.githubusercontent.com/media/b94901099/Hanzi-Steps-Images/main/stories/pangu/img_story_pangu_82.png"
      },
      {
        "id": "sent_pangu_83",
        "text": "河水嘩啦啦地流，從高山流向大海。",
